# qalam

> From raw intent to elite-grade prompts.

**qalam** is a personal prompt engineering system that transforms rough, 
unstructured prompt drafts into precision-crafted prompts — the kind used 
by the top 0.001% of Claude power users.

## Structure

- `prompts/raw/` — dump your messy drafts here
- `prompts/refined/` — optimized outputs ready to use
- `templates/` — reusable prompt frameworks by use case
- `examples/` — before/after showcase

## Philosophy

A prompt is only as good as the clarity behind it.
qalam does not add magic — it surfaces what you already know.

